settings.editor: Clean, clear and unique designs with your corporate image in mind. Whether you're interested in logo designs, marketing brochures, newsletters, drect mail pieces, trade show displays, or point-of-purchase designs, we're here to create your vision or the one you didn't know you wanted until you saw it.
Clean, clear, and unique designs with your corporate image in mind. We're here to create your vision or the one you didn't know you wanted until you saw it.

Branding is not only your Logo Design, brand and identity design convey your goals and your brand voice into visual elements.
For a successful business is important to have a great product but also show your customers that your product is the best choice and connect with them sharing the same values and vision.
That is why having a strong brand identity design is crucial for every company and I will help you build a unique brand design that connects with your values and make it relevant to your clients.

To create trust in your company is important to have graphic design assets aligned with the voice of your company.
I help you connect with your customers using Graphic Design to grab the viewer’s attention and transmitting your brand values and message using visual elements.
If you are looking for a unique graphic design style for your company and products here is my design process to help you connect with your customers.

uc_items.title: CONNECT
uc_items.text: The first step on my brand design process is to connect with you and hear your idea and goals with this project.

uc_items.title: DEFINE IDEAS AND STRATEGY
uc_items.text: Once we start talking about the project, we will discuss the idea behind your brand and what strategy we will follow to build a strong brand identity aligned with your values.

uc_items.title: RESEARCH AND COMPETENCE
uc_items.text: When we have a clear vision on the strategy to follow, the next step is to make a complete research of the market, analyze the competitors and create a buyer profile.

uc_items.title: STUDY
uc_items.text: When we have all the data required for the project, the next step is to create the first concept that reflects your brand values, message, and voice at the same time that we build a strategy to differentiate your brand from competitors.

uc_items.title: IDENTITY DESIGN
uc_items.text: Once the visual mood board and the strategy is clear it starts the designing process where I design the Logo Design for your brand and the branding elements that will support the brand.

uc_items.title: PRESENTATION
uc_items.text: When the brand identity design process is finished I send you a presentation to introduce you to the visual elements of your brand and how they connect with your audience, differentiate you from your competitors, and transmit your brand essence.

uc_items.title: IMPROVING DETAILS AND BRAND GUIDE
uc_items.text: Once the last details of the branding project are polished I send you the final files and a Brand Style Guide with all the information and guidelines on how to use your brand visual elements to create a cohesive graphic design style.

uc_items.title: CONNECT
uc_items.text: The first step in my design process for Graphic Design is to connect with you and know what are your needs.

uc_items.title: DEFINE IDEAS
uc_items.text: Once we have established the first contact, we will define your ideas with a design brief, to make clear your objectives with your graphic design project.

uc_items.title: RESEARCH
uc_items.text: Once we have clear your idea and objectives with the design I start the process of Research, collecting useful information, ideas, and inspiration to create a mood board that later will use to develop the design.

uc_items.title: BRAINSTORMING
uc_items.text: Once I already have all the information from the research and the mood board ready I start to brainstorm ideas and trying the first raw ideas that later I will develop.

uc_items.title: DEVELOPMENT
uc_items.text: Once I made the first raw test with design I choose the best options and start developing these ideas into the final design that later will present you.

uc_items.title: PRESENTATION
uc_items.text: After I finish the design process and adjust the last details of the design I will present you the final design to hear your feedback.

uc_items.title: IMPROVING DETAILS
uc_items.text: The last part of my design process is adjusting details of the graphic design project after your feedback to deliver you the best result.
